Polynomial long division gives us
\[
\begin{array}{c|ccc}
\multicolumn{2}{r}{x} & +3 \\
\cline{2-4}
2x-5 & 2x^2&+x&-13 \\
\multicolumn{2}{r}{2x^2} & -5x &   \\
