Then, calculating the distance:
\[ AB = \sqrt{(\sqrt{3} - (-\sqrt{3}))^2 + (\sqrt{3} - \sqrt{3})^2} = \sqrt{(2\sqrt{3})^2} = 2\sqrt{3}. \] 
Thus, length \( AB \) is \( \boxed{2\sqrt{3}} \).

